{
  "stem": "11000.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I remember one time, the guard said they had caught a man who had-- still had a gold ring that he had kept, and his wedding band or whatever, and he hadn't given that when he was supposed to.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And he-- this man in front of us, he just beat him to death.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "So I mean, I'm sure this man never had anything, but this-- these were the situations.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "These were the lessons that they were showing us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "This is what's happening to you if you don't obey by what we tell you to do.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And the result, of course, was that you did what you had to do, and you were just hoping and-- there were times where you really didn't think you were going to make it, and I think the fortunate thing, the lucky thing, was that we really-- the five of us kept together, and we were able to help each other and-- and how shall I say, give each other-- come on.",
      "word_count": 72
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "You know, you've kept up till now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "It's not going to last that much longer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Someday, something is gonna happen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "After all, the world can't just stand by all the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "But Gleiwitz was a very, very sad, very bad period, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think when the time came that we had to leave Gleiwitz, I don't think anybody really was sad about it.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "No matter what the outcome would be, no matter where we would go, you had seen the worse-- you know, only  can get better.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And sure enough, one morning when we came to the factory-- and this was very unusual.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "It never happened before.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Instead of one ration of bread, we got two rations of bread, and something was wrong.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
